arStrings.szText: Enemies damaged by {c_important}Kick{/c} or {c_important}Charge{/c} will explode if they are killed within the next {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds, dealing {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} damage to surrounding enemies.

Enemies damaged by {c_important}Kick{/c} or {c_important}Charge{/c} explode when killed and deal {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} damage.
